{"data":{"birthDateOn":null,"multiLocalePhoneticLastName":null,"industryV2Urn":null,"objectUrn":"urn:li:member:8273971","multiLocaleLastName":{"en_US":"Lee"},"pronounUnion":null,"multiLocaleFirstNamePronunciationHint":{},"multiLocaleLastNamePronunciationHint":{},"tempStatusExpiredAtUnion":null,"multiLocaleFirstName":{"en_US":"Nate"},"multiLocaleTempStatus":null,"contentRestrictedAnnotation":null,"companyNameOnProfileTopCardShown":true,"state":null,"publicIdentifier":"natetrustmind","trackingId":"QD56Yx+gQjeGChywO44lgg==","phoneticFirstName":null,"multiLocaleSummary":{"en_US":"I'm the founder and CEO of TrustMind. Security questionnaires are a broken relic of how third-party risk used to work. We're automating them away so teams can focus on actual risk.\n\nAfter 20+ years in security including serving as CISO at Tradeshift, a hypergrowth unicorn B2B SaaS fintech where I secured over a trillion dollars in global trade for F500 companies, I got tired of watching my team waste thousands of hours copy-pasting the same questionnaire answers they've given a hundred times.\n\nEnterprise tools charge a fortune and still make you wait days. Teams hack together solutions with ChatGPT and hit the same rough edges every time. We built TrustMind to make the problem go away.\n\nWe offer a free tier because every team deserves access to automation that actually works, not just the ones with seven-figure software budgets.\n\nMy background spans startups and the Fortune 50 in engineering, architecture, and leadership roles across Security, SRE, DevOps/Platform Engineering, IT, and CI/CD. That breadth is what makes TrustMind different. We built a product that actually handles the chaos of real-world questionnaires, not just a demo that works on the easy ones.\n\nPreviously, I also founded Cloudsec.ai to enable software-first organizations align their security and AI programs with business goals."},"firstNamePronunciationHint":null,"lastNamePronunciationHint":null,"versionTag":"383324